619
00:57:48,659 --> 00:57:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali na godišnjicu

620
00:57:51,019 --> 00:57:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] našeg vukovarskog vjenčanja

621
00:57:52,880 --> 00:57:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] vjenčamo

622
00:57:53,500 --> 00:57:55,159
