623
00:57:55,159 --> 00:57:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] Službeno u Zagrebu.

624
00:57:57,480 --> 00:57:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] i, kažem,

625
00:57:58,980 --> 00:58:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] meni su kumovi,

626
00:58:00,199 --> 00:58:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

627
00:58:00,559 --> 00:58:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] bili vukovarci.

628
00:58:01,619 --> 00:58:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jasna i Zoran Šipoš.

629
00:58:06,400 --> 00:58:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jasna koja te čuvala tamo.

630
00:58:09,219 --> 00:58:10,719
[SPEAKER_00] Jasna koja me čuvala

631
